Package: blackstone
Title: Blackstone Research and Evaluation Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zack", "Crowley", email = "zcrowley@blackstoneevaluation.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Blackstone Research and Evaluation", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: The goal of `blackstone` is to make data manipulation, analysis, and visualization 
    easier and faster for Blackstone Research and Evaluation.
    `blackstone` contains functions to create visuals with Blackstone Research and Evaluation
    branding and as well as common data cleaning, manipulation and analysis tasks
    for everyone at Blackstone Research and Evaluation.
